net), spices, natural & artificial flavor, garlic, onion and parsley) (barley, milk, oats, rye, sesame, soy, wheat) • Worcestershire sauce (water, sugars (sugar, fancy molasses), worcestershire sauce concentrate (vinegar, blackstrap molasses, glucose, water, caramel, garlic powder, sugar, spices, tamarind, natural flavour), vinegar, salt, spices, natural flavour, potassium sorbate) • Green onion • Brown sugar (cane sugar, molasses) • Garlic salt (salt, garlic powder, silicon dioxide).
